<h2>3 · Spot + Fix Bugs 🐛</h2>
<p><strong>Bug A</strong> — Must <code>interact</code> only when a lever is ahead, not every step.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">while not at_goal:
    agent.interact(FORWARD)
    if agent.detect(BLOCK, FORWARD):
        agent.turn(RIGHT_TURN)
    else:
        agent.move(FORWARD, 1)
</code></pre>
