<p><strong>Bug C</strong> — On a 3D maze the agent must climb floors. This only handles left/right/forward.</p>
<pre><code class="language-python">if agent.detect(BLOCK, FORWARD):
    agent.turn(RIGHT_TURN)
else:
    agent.move(FORWARD, 1)
</code></pre>
